posting_body: ['BEAUTIFUL UNOBSTRACTED LAKEVIEW HOME!!!', 'Conveniently located to all the Great A+ SCHOOLS.', '4 minutes drive to Elementary Gator Run, Falcon Cove and Cypress Bay.', 'Family Friendly Community.', 'Freshly painted, stainless steel appliances, beautiful open floor plan with dinning area.', 'Plenty of space for storage, walk-in closet and 2 car garage.', 'Enjoy community Pool and Play ground.', 'Plenty of natural light + spectacular sunset view.', 'Must apply to HOA for approval 3-4 wks.', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'Helping people find rentals since 2012!', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'We specialize in Broward County Rentals.', 'I can text you a list of all the rentals available in the area.', 'Fast approval, NO HOA for some properties.', 'Pet friendly for some!', 'Proof of income is the most  important thing.', 'We can help people with bad credit or no credit!', "Let me know what you're looking for and I will find the right place regardless of the situation!", 'Brittini Flinn', 'SUN OCEAN REALTY', 'NO EMAIL', 'TEXT FOR FASTEST RESPONSE:', 'show contact info', 'RENTBROWARDHOMES.COM', 'PLEASE REFER TO TYN112465361']
